high_descs: Turn to the left, walk almost all the way to the table, then turn right and face the kitchen counter.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter, closest to the backsplash.
Place the knife in the mug that is sitting on the counter.
Pick up the mug with the knife in it from the counter.
Move over to the small black table with shelves that sits to the left of the counter.
Place the mug with the knife in it on the right hand side of the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug with a knife in it to a small table.

high_descs: Turn left and the right to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the knife closest to the wall up from the counter.
Put the knife in the mug on the counter.
Pick the mug up from the counter.
Move to the left and face the black table to the left of the counter.
Put the mug down on the black table to the left of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife in it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left, turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter to the left of the cup.
Put the knife in the cup on the counter.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Walk to the black shelf to the left of the counter.
Put the cup down on the shelf to the right of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a cup and move the cup to the shelf.
